In his educational video, Andrej attempts to explain the workings of the much-talked-about AI ChatGPT. As part of his demonstration, he plans to create and train a Transformer-based character-level language model in Python, using 'Tiny Shakespeare', a dataset that comprises the entire works of Shakespeare, as a training set. He emphasizes that proficiency in Python, calculus, and statistics would be required to follow along. He aims to help his viewers understand how ChatGPT works under the hood.